metadata.name: FLØRICIDE
metadata.description:
A story formed by a discovery of longing for the meanings that arise, grow, and disappear amidst the encounters of beauty and destruction, whatever forms them in opposition, the harmony that occurs, the dynamics, and even the dilemmas that arise due to the accuracy of space and time meeting.

Based on Artwork // 5000 x 7500 px (Drawing).
Finished on 10 Sec VIDEO ART // 2720 × 4078 px.
